The Freshman;;1990;;PG;;Comedy,Crime;;6.5;;Andrew Bergman;;Marlon Brando,Matthew Broderick,Bruno Kirby,Penelope Ann Miller,Frank Whaley,Jon Polito,Paul Benedict,Richard Gant,Kenneth Welsh,Pamela Payton-Wright,BD Wong,Maximilian Schell,Bert Parks,Tex Konig,Leonardo Cimino,Gianni Russo,Warren Davis,Vera Lockwood;;Clark Kellogg is a young man starting his first year at film school in New York City. After a small time crook steals all his belongings, Clark meets Carmine "Jimmy the Toucan" Sabatini, an "importer" bearing a startling resemblance to a certain cinematic godfather. When Sabatini makes Clark an offer he can't refuse, he finds himself caught up in a caper involving endangered species and fine dining.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099615/